+#### Prefer leading comment when there is a comment on after "?" in conditional types ([#8557](https://github.com/prettier/prettier/pull/8557) by [@sosukesuzuki](https://github.com/sosukesuzuki))
+
+<!-- prettier-ignore -->
+```ts
+// Input
+type A = B extends T
+  ? // comment
+    foo
+  : bar;
+
+// Prettier stable
+type A = B extends T // comment
+  ? foo
+  : bar;
+
+// Prettier master
+type A = B extends T
+  ? // comment
+    foo
+  : bar;
+
+```
